<LegalDoc
  title="Privacy Policy — Ivory Arc Travels"
  description="How Ivory Arc Travels collects, uses and protects your personal information."
  canonical="/legal/privacy"
  heading="Privacy Policy"
>
  <p>
    This policy explains what personal information Ivory Arc Travels collects when you enquire about
    or book a journey, how we use it, and the choices you have.
  </p>

  <h2>Information we collect</h2>
  <ul>
    <li>Contact and enquiry details you share with us (for example over WhatsApp or through the estimator) — such as your name, travel dates, party size and preferences.</li>
    <li>Booking and billing information needed to confirm and deliver a journey.</li>
    <li>Payment information processed by our payment provider (Razorpay). We do not store full card details on our own systems.</li>
    <li>Basic technical and analytics data about how the site is used.</li>
  </ul>

  <h2>How we use your information</h2>
  <ul>
    <li>To plan, quote, confirm and deliver your journey.</li>
    <li>To communicate with you about your enquiry or booking.</li>
    <li>To meet legal, tax and accounting obligations.</li>
  </ul>

  <h2>Sharing</h2>
  <p>
    We share information only as needed to deliver your journey — for example with hotels, transport
    and guide partners — and with service providers such as our payment processor and hosting
    provider. We do not sell your personal information.
  </p>

  <h2>Retention</h2>
  <p>
    We keep personal information for as long as needed to provide our services and to meet legal and
    accounting requirements, then delete or anonymize it. [State your retention periods.]
  </p>

  <h2>Your rights</h2>
  <p>
    You may ask us to access, correct or delete your personal information, subject to applicable law.
    [Describe your process and any statutory rights under Indian data-protection law.]
  </p>

  <h2>Contact</h2>
  <p>For any privacy request, reach us via the details on our <a href="/contact">contact page</a>.</p>
</LegalDoc>
